{"tid":112494,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［爆音] 紅米 Note 4X 初音未來特別版","createTime":"2017-02-08T07:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T11:00:48.000Z","uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"177550876132c5de8046c48c23a60842a2bcec2b","tid":112494,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/02/07/xiaomi-redmi-note-4x-x-hatsune-miku/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2017%2F02%2F07%2Fxiaomi-redmi-note-4x-x-hatsune-miku%2F&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5Scn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b16cf36d\" target=\"_blank\">http://chinese.engadget.com/2017/02/07/xiaomi-redmi-note-4x-x-hatsune-miku/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/HMBrDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FHMBrDQ.jpg&h=663f2b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/PTDhRC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FPTDhRC.jpg&h=20f75f88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒想到關於新機紅米 Note 4X 神秘代言人的秘密，小米自己都沒有保守多久。就在昨天放出「甩蔥歌」預熱以後，今天他們就公開了「紅米 Note 4X 初音未來限量套裝」的真容。從照片中可以看到，這款手機擁有幾乎和紅米 Note 4 一樣的設計，不過用上了標誌性的初音綠色，而且背蓋下方也寫有「初音未來」字樣和限量編號。除此之外，產品的包裝自然也換用了 Miku 的主題，盒內還有對應的行動電源和保護套。"},{"pid":"f08d52b25f46c9e3da43ad8479aacd5561e3ec79","tid":112494,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"有授權？"},{"pid":"35ce76ce66e3d3ca2b005fe2430c3e2d659ab5aa","tid":112494,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"miku 被屌米強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb018d